name: Holiday Partners - Frosted Pine Spirit
description:
Happiest holiday greetings that you can give to a special person and his or her special person, too! The heavy fog rolled in on a frigid cold day … multiple layers of frost built up on these delicate white pine needles. A unique and beautiful photograph for a unique and beautiful sentiment.

Item #: HP-FPS-068

name: Holiday Partner - Island Paradise
description:
Not everyone lives or celebrates the holidays in a white snowy winter wonderland! Some lucky people celebrate in sun-soaked white-sand island paradises … such as this pleasant photo of cottages and peaceful scenery during my wonderful trip to Bermuda. Toast your love to your partner and to the holidays … island style!

Item #: CP-IP-026

name: Holiday Daughters - Joy Frosted Branch
description:
A beautiful wintertime card to give to your daughter and daughter in-law. Married or not, you love them both dearly and now you can show it. Express your feelings and sentiments of the season with a lacy frost covered pine bough displaying some of the beauties of winter.

Item #: H-DJFB-063

name: Holiday Partners - Large Frosted Pine
description:
The most gorgeous of winter’s chill in a photograph of white pine layered and layered with frost looking like it is flocked with velvet. When you touched it, the frost just disappeared, melted away with the heat of your hand. Here the tenderness of the seasons lies, peaceful and loving, in a beautiful sentiment to two people you care about dearly.

Item #: HP-LFP-067

name: Christmas Partner - Alaskan Snow
description:
There is nothing like a graceful amount of deep blanketed snow, a tall forest of pines and some very impressive mountains of Alaskan range with a touch of Alpine glow to be awe inspiring. Celebrate the grace and glow of the holiday with your partner. Place this card on the night table with perhaps some champagne and a snippet of fresh aromatic pine*. When your partner awakes Christmas morning … you fill in the rest! 

*If this is a relatively new partner, do an allergy test first … for the pine, of course! Well, at first anyway.

Item #: CP-AS-006

name: Christmas Partner - Sun and Alaskan Pine
description:
The Alaskan alpine glow of the sun breaking through the clouds onto the snow covered pine is a beautiful tribute to your partner for the Christmas holiday. Show him or her how much they really mean to you!

Item #: CP-SAP-008

name: Holiday Partner - Snow, Sun and Trees
description:
The beautiful warmth of the morning sun casting the long shadows of very tall hardwoods along a Pennsylvania farmer’s field. It is the kind of brisk morning to not leave the house (except to photograph things like these!) and to curl up and snuggle with your beloved partner for as long as you can. Enjoy the wonderful winter holidays together!

Item #: CP-SST-007

name: Christmas Partner - Frosty Plant
description:
My good friend’s front yard supplied me with this wonderful specimen of frosty winterized looking plant. Up close, it takes on a rather festive and unique life of it’s own. Use this unusual botanical to wish your fondest companion a wonderful Christmas this year. Be different!

Item #: CP-FP-025

name: Holiday Partner - Snow Fall
description:
A fun graphic Happy Holidays to a special couple from you! A beautiful snowy winter wonderland to simply express your best wishes for a wonderful holiday season. For once, the snow fall was soft and gentle in Bristol, NY for this photo. It creates a perfect winter scene for this greeting for your friends and loved ones.

Item #: CP-SF-022

name: Holiday Partner - Snowy Drive
description:
The snow covered drive to our family camp in the Finger Lakes, NY, provides the perfect back drop for coming home and being with loved ones. Enjoy being back home with your special loved one and let them know your anticipation for their arrival with this snowy scene and sentiment.

Item #: CP-SD-024

name: Holiday Partner - Tree with Berries
description:
Celebrate the bounty of the holidays with your beloved partner with this card! This year’s rains have created bountiful crops of beautiful berries on these colorful flowering dogwood trees here in Pennsylvania. The holidays in the past were celebrated by giving thanks for your abundance and being surrounded by your loved ones. This very pretty greeting symbolizes both for you.

Item #: CP-TWB-021

name: Christmas Partner - Winter Stream
description:
A very special merry Christmas message to your loved one with an attention getting graphic and a beautiful natural winter scene in Pennsylvania. As fresh as the bubbling stream with crisp snow laced trees and clean morning air, this card simply says, “I love you” as the most wonderful gift of the holiday season.

Happy Anniversary to your dads with a very silly refreshing sentiment with love and a dose of ADD! Let’s face it … you would love a pond and so would your fathers. What a perfect way of getting the idea across to them and sending them a cute tribute to their special day.

Item #: AF-FPD-028

name: Anniversary Partner - Perfect Pears
description:
More ripe golden pears so perfectly placed on a beautiful silk scarf. Symbolically representing togetherness and the abundance from their perfect relationship. Celebrate your anniversary together with this unique and beautifully captured sentiment. Serve with poached pears and champagne!

Item #: AP-PP-027

name: Anniversary Parents - Red Classic Car
description:
Classic 1950 style cars are just so cool … especially bright red ones with lots of gleaming chrome and big white walls! Have fun celebrating your parents’ milestone with the appropriate sentiment from the two of you!

Item #: AP-RCC-045

name: ﻿Anniversary Parents - Purple Bouquet
description:
Happy Anniversary to parents from son, son-in-law and family! How fun when it is all spelled out like that! Wish your parents with the appropriate signature a very happy day for their milestone together.

Item #: AP-PB-046

name: Anniversary Parents - Purple Floral Reflection
description:
Happy Anniversary to parents from daughter and daughter-in-law! Wish your parents a very happy day for their milestone together with the appropriate signature card. A pretty bouquet to lighten their hearts from the two of you.

Item #: AP-PFR-047

name: Anniversary Parents - Summer Lake
description:
The beauty of golden day lilies and a cool mountain lake on one gorgeous day … you can hear the birds and the breeze. Wish your parents well for their anniversary milestone with a perfect sentiment and the perfect greeting!

Item #: AP-SL-044

name: Birthday Partner - Alaska Mountains
description:
Happy real BIG birthday to your wonderful “bigger than life” partner! Help your companion celebrate a milestone birthday or just celebrate in a large fashion no matter what the age with a very pretty card with a panoramic landscape. If you have ever been to Alaska, you will know by what I mean by BIG!

Item #: BP-AM-010

name: Birthday Partner - Amusement Park
description:
You can just hear the wild screaming looking at this crazy amusement park ride! Be silly and celebrate your fun partner’s look on life with this silly birthday card. Actually, it probably is more serious than that, I’m trying to keep it light hearted more so than dead on accurate. Oh, well! Spend the day playing like kids anyway!

Item #: BP-AP-011

name: Birthday Partner - Autumn Road
description:
Celebrate a milestone for your partner with colorful scenery from a Pennsylvania back road in Autumn. Think of how the roads in our life are very similar to the road of life and how they intertwine themselves with our partners. This beautiful image speaks of good times for him or her with the road being so smooth and beautiful.

name: Coming Out - Alaska Waterfall
description:
Nature knows where to go and to follow its own course no matter how much mankind will attempt to interrupt her along the way. Seems to echo one’s own way with one’s own destiny. This rather tender, but strong out bound feeling, comes from a rather large waterfall tumbling down an island mountainside in the great wilderness of Alaska. Delicacy and strength are usually always interesting companions. Celebrate inwardly and outwardly with joy!

name: Coming Out - Delicate Nature
description:
Celebrate with a special someone their delicate bloom! A very pretty coming out card of Maine’s Acadia national Park’s wild flowers growing their lovely way out of the toughest of granite on a very foggy day. The sentiment is sweet, yet supportive and simply implies the promise of favorable results to happen when someone shows strength and tenderness!

Item #: CO-DN-005

name: Coming Out - Glacier
description:
Wooo Hooooo! You feel as if you are on top of the world when you are up on a glacier. Nothing encloses around you, the sun sparkles bright and everything is so far away. Honor the joyous occasion with your friend or loved one with this perfect on top of the world sentiment. (Note: I will never figure out how I got this person to look like Gumby in this photo!) Enjoy!

Item #: CO-G-018

name: Coming Out - Train Tunnel
description:
A truly intimidating trip through a long train tunnel in Alaska can make you gasp! And, suddenly, from being so enclosed and confined … You are OUT! Into the big expansive landscape. It truly takes your breath completely away with the experience. Much like coming out; take a few breaths of the clear air and realize that you have made it! Celebrate your friend or loved one’s coming out with a special and appropriately clever sentiment.

name: Coming Out - Orange Ford Fairlane
description:
Celebrate a Coming Out with a beauty! This invites a ride through life the way it should be. A classically restored juicy orange Ford with a slick orange steering wheel and soft creamy leather seats … go for it! Put the top down and let more than just the wind go through your hair! Enjoy!

Item #: CO-OFF-048

name: Coming Out - Red Leaf
description:
Welcome a friend or family member with a single beautiful red leaf that stands out boldly from its background of moss and rocks. Let them know you support them and praise them for their big milestone. Just like on a walk in the fall … your eye always goes to those bright red leaves that glow! Hurray!

Item #: CO-RL-053

name: Union Partner - Alpine Glow Reflections
description:
Lake Louise, Alaska at twilight … serene, calm and breathtakingly beautiful. Symbolizing the reflection and mirroring of each other in an admirable and refined relationship. A wonderful romantic way of telling her that you want to be with her for the rest of your life!

Item #: UP-AGR-013

name: Union Partner - Beach Stroll
description:
I have always felt the most poignant thoughts of the people closest to me when I’m all alone. It lets you take a quiet inventory of the situation from a slightly different angle. Thus this card. Just knowing that someone loves you that deeply allows you to see light when it is dark, music when there is silence, etc., etc. Ask him to marry you with the deepest of feelings and love!

Item #: UP-BS-015

name: Union Partner - Seaside Sunset
description:
A beautiful poignant sentiment to share how you feel about him and your futures together. The calm sea, the strolling easy figure on the beach, the wilds of the snow capped mountains over looking Homer, Alaska are in the gleam of the sun. The overlay of descriptive words to support your perceptions of his personality and ambitions. Celebrate your feelings together!

Item #: UP-SS-014

name: Union Partner - Yellow Iris
description:
This gorgeous card is a close up photograph of the inside of a beautiful golden yellow iris with a gentle over lay of words describing every kind of female. This explosion of a bloom is worthy of stating your commitment and passion to each other. Thrill her with the tender sentiment that she is your everything to you … and more! Celebrate your engagement with a golden glow!

Item #: UP-YI-012

name: Wedding Brides - Blue Convertible
description:
Love is free wheeling, cruising along with your beloved new wife by your side! Celebrate their wonderful wedding with a unique kind of sentiment and feelings. There’s room for two right now … and maybe more in the future to fill the back seat. Celebrate!

Item #: WB-BC-050

name: Wedding Brides - White Roses
description:
The glow of creamy white roses always reminds us of beautiful brides on their wedding day. This is wonderful acknowledgment of your love and caring for them and, also, their lovely day celebrating their union. Make it real special for those two beautiful women!

Item #: WB-WR-042

name: Wedding Grooms - Mountain Laurel
description:
Congratulations to the lovely couple! Mountain Laurel buds are bursting open like fireworks to create the sentiment of celebration for this fabulous event. Send your best to the two hansome gentlemen and to the the happiest of Mr. and Mr.’s days!

Item #: WG-ML-043

name: Wedding Grooms - Red Convertible
description:
Tired of the typical flowers?! Get them cruising together in one hot classic red convertible! Celebrate the big day for these two lovely gentlemen in a completely unique style. Together now means traveling the rest of your lives with each other side by side … and, of course, taking turns driving!

Item #: WG-RC-054
